@startuml Registration Check Flow

title Dynamic View - Use Case 1 Registration Check (Async External Enrichment)

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 25
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ResponseMessageBelowArrow true

actor Lawyer
participant "REST API" as API
participant "Text Check Service" as TextService
participant "Embedding Model" as Model
participant "Embedding Dataset" as Dataset
participant "Search Indexes" as Indexes
database "Trademark DB" as DB
participant "Async Job Queue" as Queue
participant "External Online Search Worker" as Worker
participant "External Online Sources" as Sources
participant "Result Delivery Service" as Delivery
participant "Similarity Engine" as Similarity
participant "Ranking Engine" as Ranking

Lawyer -> API: Submit naming + Nice classes
API -> API: Validate request
API -> API: Orchestrate workflow
API -> API: Normalize naming input
API -> TextService: Run text-only internal check with canonical input

TextService -> DB: Filter candidates by Nice classes
DB --> TextService: Candidate ids from trademark DB

par Semantic search
  TextService -> Model: Generate embedding for input naming
  Model --> TextService: Query embedding
  TextService -> Dataset: Find nearest semantic candidates
  Dataset --> TextService: Semantic shortlist
else Phonetic and text search
  TextService -> Indexes: Search by phonetic and text keys
  Indexes --> TextService: Phonetic/text shortlist
end

TextService -> TextService: Merge candidate pools

loop For each candidate
  TextService -> Similarity: Calculate detailed similarity features
  Similarity --> TextService: Semantic, phonetic, text, graphic, legal features
end

TextService -> Ranking: Build final similarity percentage and sort results
Ranking --> TextService: Top-200 internal ranked conflicts
API -> Queue: Create async external search job
Queue --> Worker: Deliver job
Worker -> Sources: Search online external sources
Sources --> Worker: External candidate set
Worker -> Ranking: Build Top-200 external ranking
Ranking --> Worker: Top-200 external ranked conflicts
Worker -> Delivery: Send delayed external result set
Delivery --> API: Top-200 external results (later)
API --> Lawyer: External enrichment update

TextService --> API: Top-200 internal result
API --> Lawyer: Top-200 internal results (fast)

note right of TextService
Responsibility: text similarity only.
No external workflow orchestration.
end note

@enduml

@startuml Text Infringement Check Flow

title Use Case 2 - Text Infringement Check

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 25
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ResponseMessageBelowArrow true

actor Lawyer
participant "REST API" as API
participant "Text Check Service" as TextService
database "Trademark DB" as DB
participant "Async Job Queue" as Queue
participant "External Online Search Worker" as Worker
participant "External Online Sources" as Sources
participant "Result Delivery Service" as Delivery
participant "Similarity Engine" as Similarity

Lawyer -> API: Submit protected naming + suspicious naming
API -> API: Validate request
API -> API: Orchestrate workflow
API -> API: Normalize protected naming
API -> API: Normalize suspicious naming
API -> TextService: Run text-only infringement check with canonical inputs

TextService -> DB: Find Top-200 internal candidates for suspicious naming
DB --> TextService: Candidate list
loop For each internal candidate
  TextService -> Similarity: Compare protected naming with candidate
  Similarity --> TextService: Similarity score
end
TextService -> TextService: Build Top-200 internal ranking
API -> Queue: Create async external search job
Queue --> Worker: Deliver job

Worker -> Sources: Search online external sources for suspicious naming
Sources --> Worker: External candidate set
loop For each external candidate
  Worker -> Similarity: Compare protected naming with external candidate
  Similarity --> Worker: Similarity score
end
Worker -> Worker: Build Top-200 external ranking
Worker -> Delivery: Send delayed external result set
Delivery --> API: Top-200 external results (later)
API --> Lawyer: External enrichment update

TextService --> API: Top-200 internal comparison result
API --> Lawyer: Top-200 internal results (fast) + similarity explanation

note right of TextService
Responsibility: text similarity only.
No external workflow orchestration.
end note

@enduml

@startuml Logo Comparison Flow

title Use Case 3 - Logo Infringement Check (Optional)

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 25
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ResponseMessageBelowArrow true

actor Lawyer
participant "REST API" as API
participant "Logo Check Service" as LogoService
participant "Logo Preprocessing" as LogoPreprocess
participant "Logo Feature Extractor" as FeatureExtractor
participant "Visual Similarity Engine" as VisualSimilarity
database "Trademark DB" as DB
participant "Async Job Queue" as Queue
participant "External Online Search Worker" as Worker
participant "External Online Sources" as Sources
participant "Result Delivery Service" as Delivery

Lawyer -> API: Submit reference logo + suspicious logo
API -> API: Validate request
API -> LogoService: Start logo comparison

LogoService -> LogoPreprocess: Normalize both logo files
LogoPreprocess --> LogoService: Prepared visual inputs

LogoService -> FeatureExtractor: Extract visual features and text-in-logo if available
FeatureExtractor --> LogoService: Feature vectors

LogoService -> DB: Find Top-200 internal logo candidates
DB --> LogoService: Internal logo candidates
loop For each internal logo candidate
  LogoService -> VisualSimilarity: Compare reference logo with internal candidate
  VisualSimilarity --> LogoService: Visual similarity score
end
LogoService -> LogoService: Build Top-200 internal ranking
API -> Queue: Create async external logo search job
Queue --> Worker: Deliver job

Worker -> Sources: Search online external sources for logo candidates
Sources --> Worker: External logo candidates
loop For each external logo candidate
  Worker -> VisualSimilarity: Compare reference logo with external candidate
  VisualSimilarity --> Worker: Visual similarity score
end
Worker -> Worker: Build Top-200 external ranking
Worker -> Delivery: Send delayed external logo result set
Delivery --> API: Top-200 external logo results (later)
API --> Lawyer: External logo enrichment update

LogoService --> API: Top-200 internal logo results
API --> Lawyer: Top-200 internal logo results (fast) + visual summary

@enduml

